{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Resource_pool.Make</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"soteria","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Soteria","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Soteria_std","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Resource_pool","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Make","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[{"title":"Parameters","href":"#parameters","children":[]},{"title":"Signature","href":"#signature","children":[]}],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"","content":"<h2 id=\"parameters\"><a href=\"#parameters\" class=\"anchor\"></a>Parameters</h2><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec parameter anchored\" id=\"argument-1-R\"><a href=\"#argument-1-R\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> </span><span><a href=\"argument-1-R/index.html\">R</a></span><span> : <a href=\"../module-type-Resource/index.html\">Resource</a></span></code></div></div><h2 id=\"signature\"><a href=\"#signature\" class=\"anchor\"></a>Signature</h2><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-resource\"><a href=\"#type-resource\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> resource</span><span> = <a href=\"argument-1-R/index.html#type-t\">R.t</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-t\"><a href=\"#type-t\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> t</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-pool\"><a href=\"#type-pool\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> pool</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-auth\"><a href=\"#type-auth\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> auth</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-create_pool\"><a href=\"#val-create_pool\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> create_pool : <span>unit <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"#type-pool\">pool</a></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Create a new empty pool.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-acquire\"><a href=\"#val-acquire\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> acquire : <span><a href=\"#type-pool\">pool</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> * <a href=\"#type-auth\">auth</a></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Acquire a resource from the pool. If an unused resource is available, it is returned. Otherwise, a new resource is created. Returns the pooled resource and an auth token that must be used for subsequent operations.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-release\"><a href=\"#val-release\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> release : <span><a href=\"#type-pool\">pool</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"#type-auth\">auth</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Release a resource back to the pool. The auth token must match the one returned by <code>acquire</code>. Raises <code>Pool_invalid_auth</code> if the auth token is invalid.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-handle\"><a href=\"#val-handle\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> handle : <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> int</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Get the handle of the pooled resource. It is a unique identifier for the resource within the pool.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-apply\"><a href=\"#val-apply\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> apply : <span><span class=\"label\">auth</span>:<a href=\"#type-auth\">auth</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span>(<span><a href=\"#type-resource\">resource</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Access the underlying resource. The auth token must match the current valid token for this resource. Raises <code>Pool_invalid_auth</code> if the resource has been released.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-total_resources\"><a href=\"#val-total_resources\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> total_resources : <span><a href=\"#type-pool\">pool</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> int</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-available_resources\"><a href=\"#val-available_resources\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> available_resources : <span><a href=\"#type-pool\">pool</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> int</span></code></div></div>"}